HEADWORD: Introspect
<hw>In`tro*spect"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>introspectus</ets>, p. p. <ets>introspicere</ets> to look into;
<ets>intro</ets> within + <ets>specere</ets> to look. See
<er>Spy</er>.]</ety> <def>To look into or within; to view the inside
